    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver\u2019s specimen featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via a mechanical limited-slip differential. The chassis remains composed thanks to a reinforced subframe and a refreshed suspension setup that maintains factory-spec kinematics. Recent service includes a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul, ensuring optimal variable valve timing and torque delivery. This is a mechanically robust example of the ultimate driving machine, offering the raw, analog feedback and balanced weight distribution that defines the M-division's golden era.",
