      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a reliable companion. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years\u2014perfect for someone who needs a dependable set of wheels without any fuss! It drives great and is totally ready for its next adventure. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take a look!",
